{
  "stem": "1828.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had to laugh, and-- and we had so many talented people that spoke about literature to us at night when was in our own room, who spoke about art, and who-- and all their experiences.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother spoke about the first war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And there were not many mothers left at that point.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There were only two.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in the end, I think she was the only one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was, if my father was 49, she was 48 at that point.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was having a tough time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- we inched our way little by little, various means of transportation, because they needed the trucks, and they needed the-- they were doing badly.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we rarely-- we rarely have so much-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] Anyway, we arrived on the-- we left Germany-- I mean, these German camps, on the 7th of April, 1945.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we started by truck, and by various means, to go further inland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I don't know exactly when we arrived in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's-- if we left on the 7th, we-- it may have taken two or three days to get there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But when we arrived there, that was the horror of horrors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a-- an epidemic of typhoid going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you ever saw newsreels with piles of bodies and utter misery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, beyond description.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We arrived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We felt like we were, you know, in good shape compared to these people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were lying on the ground, half alive, half dead, whatever, without any attention given to them whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was covered with people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Inside, outside everywhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And my sister claims we were in-- in Bergen-Belsen for a week.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I think it was three days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I mean I just don't-- it was all one big blur.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
